Orlando Bloom and Miranda Kerr still love each other
Actor Orlando Bloom and model Miranda Kerr intend to go their separate ways.
In an interview, however, Bloom said that he and Kerr still love each other.
Miranda Kerr and Orlando Bloom are parents of two-year-old Flynn.
Actor Orlando Bloom has, commented on the separation from his wife, supermodel Miranda Kerr.
In an interview with U.S. journalist Katie Couric, which on Friday (local time) to be broadcast, Bloom said, "that life is sometimes not exactly as we plan for it or hope for."
Kerr and he loved each other still, said the 36-year-old.
"We will support each other and love them as parents of Flynn".
Kerr and Bloom have been married since 2010, in 2011 their son Flynn was born.
